<H1> 273 B.C.    Olympiad 126.4</H1>
<BR> Consuls: C. Fabius M.f. <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/l/licinus.html#1">Licinus,</A> C. Claudius M.f. <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/c/canina.html#1">Canina</A> (II) 
<BR>   Athenian <A CLASS="help" HREF="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archon_of_Athens">archon</A>: Glaucippus
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
